# Dragon fight event hooks (syntax-safe)

on spawn of ender dragon:
    set {event.dragon.active} to true
    broadcast "&5&l[END EVENT] &dThe Ender Dragon has awakened."
    wait 10 seconds
    broadcast "&5&l[END EVENT] &dDragon interference is active. PvP remains disabled during the event."

on death of ender dragon:
    set {event.dragon.active} to false
    set {event.glitch.active} to false
    broadcast "&a&l[END EVENT] The Ender Dragon has been defeated!"
